"2019-11-10T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"好柒煩<br />\n永遠唔好提啲垃圾當幫忙得唔得？"},{"pid":"1bf69e09ea439e55dd560d0e2c0263c0ebdeec7d","tid":1702642,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c0f3ec731b72b2d9733b2d44d29a318db930d926","tid":1702642,"uid":152230,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:18:30.000Z","msg":"極度懷疑係backup佬本人 邊有人開post凈係狙擊同一個人咁耐 除左因為有仇 我諗唔到有乜原因"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"我真人是認識backup兄弟，但我不是他。"},{"pid":"2d589979f94244a74df27607c6df9343834df35d","tid":1702642,"uid":129491,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"收到內幕消息其實達哥唔係因為連登仔反佢先唔出黎直播  其實係因為佢一早搵夠  再加又識誠仔 美斯呢d勁人  佢一早搵左夠佢用幾世既錢  依家係日本同緊結衣bb過緊退休生活  基於佢餘生都唔會係香港住  所以香港既野佢都唔想理了  仲叫我同你地講放過佢"},{"pid":"9afafbbafc9ff40d042c2bfc4557c1581f3c1b74","tid":1702642,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b1ae6c101bbab9714fa1c0e8bd1d3fcbca75071c","tid":1702642,"uid":3270,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T23:49:42.000Z","msg":"你係咪on9嫁<br />\n你覺得d人係因為佢打機廢分析唔好先反佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關珍唔珍惜咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"抗爭與否為既係香港<br />\n關其他人出唔出聲咩事<br />\n馮盈盈夠多人J啦 <br />\n咁唔通馮盈盈就要出聲 <br />\n唔出聲就圍佢老母呀?"},{"pid":"4a339b87f2dd829955e4064cfe5c50c1f709b8c7","tid":1702642,"uid":181675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5481a73b9c2b7b187c1e64f34fd239d87e7f7869","tid":1702642,"uid":142878,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T00:21:23.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗標題做:<br />\n請珍惜 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>哥布林</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e61b860cb4a1589b072a9517b7f103644c75e6","tid":1702642,"uid